(517, 'Red Alert 3: Uprising features four new mini-campaigns, giving players a deeper dive into the storylines of the Soviets, the Allies, the Empire of the Rising Sun and a unique campaign centered on the origins of everyoneÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s favorite psionic Japanese schoolgirl commando, Yuriko Omega.'),
