(594, 'From the team that re-imagined The Secret of Monkey IslandÃ¢â€žÂ¢, comes Lucidity, an addictive puzzle platformer set in the surreal childlike dreamscapes of the little girl Sofi. In this challenging puzzler, itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s your task to keep Sofi safe as she drifts deeper into the strange new world of her dreams.'),
(595, 'Star Wars The Clone Wars: Republic Heroes lets Star Wars fans young and old live out the sweeping galactic adventures of the Clone Wars. For the first time ever, players can fight as their favorite Jedi and Clone Troopers from the preeminent animated television...'),
