(900, 'When Quinns new travel business hits a snag, she needs Flos patented elbow grease to help renovate and run hotels all over DinerTown&trade;! As Flo, you will deliver guests luggage, drop off room service and provide extra towels, blankets and anything else they may need to stay happy and leave big tips!'),
