(913, 'While on a well deserved vacation, Professor Fizzwizzles investigation of a strange volcano has landed him in a Molten Mystery! Now its up to you to master exciting new gadgets, outwit the Bat-Bots, and vanquish a truly cunning villain! Can the professor count on you to help?'),
