(1669, 'Far Cry 3: Blood Dragon is THE Kick-Ass Cyber Shooter.Welcome to an 80\'s vision of the future. The year is 2007 and you are Sargent Rex Colt, a Mark IV Cyber Commando. Your mission: get the girl, kill the baddies, and save the world.'),
