(1796, 'The worlds speediest homage/roast to JRPGs! Can you save the world in 30 seconds? Get a quest, find those in need, fight through dungeons, earn cash, get cool loot and level up until YOU&gt;EVIL. Dont have enough time? Pay the Goddess to reset the clock and try again! Over 100 mini-JRPGs for you to test your might with!'),
(1797, 'At the Gates is an indie strategy game from Jon Shafer, designer of Civilization 5. You are a dark age lord building a kingdom to replace the crumbling Roman Empire. Manage your clans, explore the landscape around you, harvest its resources, and build a mighty economic and military machine.'),
