(1819, 'FBI agent Erica Reed has an uncanny talent: she can see the past and piece together how a crime unfolded. But not even this sixth sense could save her younger brother, Scott, from a brutal serial killer. Three years later, the investigation into ScottÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s murder has gone cold -- but EricaÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s work has only just begun.'),
