(2574, 'Tango Fiesta is a top-down cooperative shooter for 1-4 players. Imagine the events from every single 80Ã¢â‚¬â„¢s action film ever made actually happened to one guy - well you &amp; up to 3 friends get to blast, shoot &amp; knife your way through procedurally generated levels as the ultimate one (or 2, 3, or 4) man army!'),
