(2603, 'A Story About My Uncle is a first person platforming adventure game about a boy who searches for his lost uncle, and ends up in a world he couldn\'t imagine existed. The movement is a crucial part of the games core gameplay focusing on swinging through the world with a grappling hook that gives the player a wonderful sense of speed and...'),
