(3045, 'Thrust into the role of &quot;The Seed of Prophecy,&quot; players travel deep into the living castle, in hopes of defeating the evil that dwells within the dreaded Warlock Lord.'),
(3046, 'Fenix\'s village was decimated by a huge explosion, leaving only our hero and the mysterious Oktarus. As Fenix, track down this shadowy villain through nine worlds, defeating brutal bosses and hundreds of minions bent on your destruction.'),
(3047, 'So who is haunting the schoolhouse, taking the toys and practically scaring the scales off all the guppies?'),
