(3974, 'This is the River City sports challenge! The Rule is simple, be the # 1 in 4 events by all means. Thats it! Hitting and kicking? Of course! Wooden swords dumbbells and even bombs are available to use. The great sports challenge where anythings possible has just begun!!!'),
(3975, 'Create a character and fight your enemies in 2D MMORPG with your friends. Huge open world, guild castles, free PvP, arena, battles between Alliances, Guilds, Dungeons and jolly holidays await!'),
(3976, 'In the exciting visual adventure Mystery of Neuschwanstein, you will find all of the ingredients needed for a thrilling mystery adventure: a world famous castle, the mysterious, unexplained death of a fairy-tale king, and plenty of anonymous clues pointing to a whole web of dark conspiracies!'),
(3977, 'Windward is an action-filled multiplayer sandbox game that puts you in control of a ship sailing the high seas of a large procedurally-generated world.'),
(3978, 'The names Glyph. Sam Glyph. Private eye. I was outta work...I hadnt busted a case in months. I was looking for a job...turns out, it was a job that would find ME...'),
(3979, 'Demolish your friends with hundreds of upgradable weapons shot from your customizable tank in this action-packed online multiplayer tanks game. Earn XP to level up and unlock new tanks, weapons, and gear. Fight against or alongside your friends for strategic team or free-for-all matches.'),
(3980, 'Its a highly competitive 2D arcade game where you move the earth to a safe place by warping the space around. Thanks to educational elements you will learn about the universe in an entertaining way. In Space Warp patience, skills and perfect timing is the key to beat your friends.'),
(3981, 'If My Heart Had Wings is an animated visual novel presenting a lovely and bittersweet tale of youth. Take on the role of Aoi Minase in this romantic-comedy as he meets various young girls in his hometown and works together with them to revive their schoolÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s glider-flying Ã¢â‚¬Å“Soaring ClubÃ¢â‚¬Â in order to realize their shared dream of flight.'),
