(3991, 'In a free, add-on mod for Killing Floor, created by David Hensley (with help from Killing Floor originator, Alex Quick), you can fight off the bizarre and warped toys of someones nightmare, that are hell-bent on finishing you off. All the standard Zeds are replaced with evil toys, set in the Devils Dollhouse map.'),
(3992, 'Deep Eclipse: New Space Odyssey is the ultimate space thriller in the best tradition of the genre. Youre the pilot of a space fighter, accidentally catapulted into a parallel universe populated by hostile alien creatures; and theyre not happy to see you! To get out of this hell, do your best, to destroy hordes of enemies.'),
(3993, 'The second game about making games! Care for and build relationships with your teammates! Now with an in-depth game development system, more story (just like you asked for), and more...'),
(3994, 'Go back in time and experience, The Fabulous Fifties, in a game that recalls scenarios, vehicles and street races of the legendary 50\'s films. Customize your car and compete in 8 different race modes, through five completely different 50\'s themed areas and become the King of the Road.'),
(3995, 'The worms are back in their most destructive game yet. With a gorgeous, hand-drawn 2D look, brand new weapons, the introduction of crafting, vehicles and buildings plus the return of some much-loved classic weapons and gameplay, Worms W.M.D is the best worms experience ever.'),
(3996, 'A desperate, savage survival experience full of stunning visuals, dynamic creatures, and a haunting soundtrack.'),
(3997, 'Gloria Victis is a MMORPG with an emphasis on realism, set in a low-fantasy medieval open world. Enjoy MMO with skill-based non-target combat, open PVP with territory control, deep crafting system and player-driven economy all that served with beautiful graphics and immersive atmosphere.'),
(3998, 'You\'re a castaway stranded in the middle of nowhere. The storm is gone, the worst certainly not. Look for food and resources, craft gear, make a shelter. These are the basics, you will need much more to stay alive on this cut-off-the-world, yet not desert island. Build and burn, sail and explore, stay out of reach!'),
