(4001, 'Collect all the Ice Cream Crystals and marry Princess Cheesecake!'),
(4002, 'With her telekinesis, unorthodox use of torture instruments, a knack for improvisation and the help of a shady fox she makes her way from the peaks of Glass Mountain to the deepest dungeon.'),
