(4005, 'HOW FAR WILL YOU GO TO SAVE YOUR ONLY DAUGHTERS LIFE?'),
(4006, 'Ahoy mateys! From the Mind of Sid Meier, The Golden Age of Buccaneering has returned with Pirates! Gold!'),
