(5238, 'Join Nikola Orelov in his search for redemption as you journey through an iconic, propaganda art style Russia in 2.5D gameplay. Survive the aftermath of October Revolution &amp; travel accross Russia. Experience the thrill of being a stealthy Assassin in an exclusive modern setting.'),
