(5252, 'This is a heavily extended version of one of the most famous roguelike games of the 80Ã¢â‚¬â„¢s named LARN. Your choice is to find a magic elixier for your daughters recovery. Therefore you have to explore a lot of unknown caves, filled with monsters, demons and traps. Good luck! You may need it!'),
(5253, 'It\'s 1984, and in the basement of a quiet arcade store somewhere in the UK, an experimental arcade machine is gathering dust.Unravel the mysteries of the cabinet in this evolving, retro sci-fi experience.'),
