(5286, 'Get ready for intense 2D arcade fighting. Spirit of old-school fighting games is back with Slashers: The Power Battle. Inspired by the classic fighting game series, Slashers: The Power Battle delivers it all - itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s fast; itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s full on; itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s tactical; itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s online and itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s FUN!'),
