(5663, 'Tompi Jones is a fun platform game in 2.5d inspired in classic platform games. You can play across six worlds between jungles, forests, medieval villages, Aztec pyramids, castles and cemeteries. You must avoid the traps and defeat your enemies with projectile weapons, fighting with the sword or with special items.'),
(5664, 'For the first time, bus, tram and train are simulated extremely realistic in a single game and you can drive them, build them or create the world around. LOTUS simulation will never be the same!'),
