(5728, 'Pixel Space is a 2D entertaining indie game where you are a ship in an infinite space and you can do quests, kill enemies in a waves system, customize your ship, buy weapons and lot of upgrades, each weapon has at least two paths of upgrades so you can play how you like.'),
