(5731, 'Real-Time-Strategy game based on great Indian epic Ramayana.'),
(5732, 'Football Mogul 2014 is the 11th version of the addictive football simulation game from the makers of Baseball Mogul.This version includes rosters and player ratings for opening weekend of the 2013-2014 season. Enjoy controlling your football franchise in any year from 1970 to 2013.'),
