(6857, 'Experience the real MotoGPÃ¢â€žÂ¢! 18 tracks and the official 2015 liveries are waiting for you in the MotoGPÃ¢â€žÂ¢15 Compact, offering you the chance to race with your MotoGPÃ¢â€žÂ¢ heroes. Dont miss this opportunity!'),
