(7203, 'From the makers of Heavenly Sword, Enslaved: Odyssey to the West, and DmC: Devil May Cry, comes a warriorÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s brutal journey into myth and madness. Set in the Viking age, a broken Celtic warrior embarks on a haunting vision quest into Viking Hell to fight for the soul of her dead lover.'),
(7204, 'Raining Blobs is a challenging, fast-paced arcade puzzle game based around matching falling blocks, featuring adorable anime-style pixelart! Prove that you have what it takes to survive the endless blob rain with up to 16 players!'),
(7205, 'Nightmare on Azathoth is a dark game, in which you might not want to find the truth. Manage your base, scavenge, collect memory fragments, and collect resources to power up your spaceship to escape this planet. Death only brings an endless time loop, that restarts everything on the 4th day.'),
(7206, 'Crashnauts is a hard-hitting 2D Arena Shooter for 2-6 players local or online. Crush your enemies with your Crashpod or obliterate them with an array of satisfying weaponry. Simple at first but boasting deep mechanics, Crashnauts delivers fun for players of any skill level.'),
(7207, 'Step into the epic adventure of the legendary pirate Captain Henry Morgan. Inspired by true events from 16th century, Caribbean Odyssey is a beautiful tale of loyalty, love, betrayal and revenge. Explore a lavish and colorful world of secrets in 2.5D.'),
(7208, '5089 is a deep &amp; complex action RPG featuring strong sandbox roots. VR is supported, but not required. Watch the tutorial &amp; VR videos next to the trailer! Everything is procedurally generated, like terrain, enemies, weapons, items &amp; quests. Planet Xaxs war rages on... how is that possible?'),
