(7266, 'The stars are going out. A team is sent to find out why. They discover the cause and try to stop it. They donÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t make it out alive. Caretaker Retribution is a 6DOF shooter for PC and Mac that also works on HTC Vive and Oculus Rift.'),
