(7269, 'The Final Frontier: Space Simulator is a new kind of space simulator, we want to bring some cool new features and joy to the space simulator genre. We want to have 3 modules (Story Mode, Online Battles, and Online Universe). We want you to be immersed into the unknown galaxy. We will hope to see you in The Final Frontier!'),
