(7273, 'Vehicle Simulator is an open world flying/sailing simulator with accurate physics and dynamics, simulating well the various boats, planes and land vehicles included. The game allows the user to modify and experiment with scenery making and vehicle design by way of extreme modability, with a large library of existing mods and add-ons.'),
(7274, 'You are Bixby, an agent within the bureaucratic metropolis known as the Ministry Of Order. As Lounge Districts go-to detective, take a stroll through a retro-future so analog itll make your head spin.'),
