(7687, 'Some say youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re only as old as you feel. Shmups Skill Test says youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re only as old as you shoot! Shmups Skill Test is a clever way to evaluate your shmup skills in the form of a &quot;gamer age&quot;. Challenge and unlock shoot-Ã¢â‚¬â„¢em-up-based minigames in a gauntlet of shmup nostalgia goodness.'),
