(7689, 'Memoranda is a 2D point and click adventure game inspired by author Haruki MurakamiÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s surreal short stories.The game tells the story of a young lady who gradually realizes that she is forgetting her own name. But is she really losing her memory?'),
(7690, 'Listen, rate and share more than 6.000 songs created in Rytmik Ultimate stored on Rytmik Cloud.'),
(7691, 'Z. Year One is a crowdfunded, single-player CCG that combines select elements of tabletop classics with a horror movie atmosphere and cinematic imagery on every card!'),
(7692, 'If there was a robot that could laugh, cry and smile. ...Does it have a soul?'),
(7693, 'The Music Room is an award nominated expressive MIDI controller. It combines virtual reality instruments and inspiring spaces. Unlike keyboard MIDI controllers, The Music Room allows you to strum, slide, bend and drum naturally and expressively.'),
