(7876, '2Dark is a stealth adventure game developed by FrÃƒÂ©dÃƒÂ©rick Raynal, the pioneer of survival horror games and creator of Alone in the DarkÃ‚Â®. Make your way through the lairs of psychopaths, unravel intrigue where madness mingles with horror, and, above all, save the kids!'),
(7877, 'Rusty Lake Hotel an eerie point-and-click adventure developed by the creators of the intriguing Cube Escape series.'),
(7878, 'Take part in the famous &quot;Rush for Gold&quot; in Alaska!'),
