(7900, 'Nadia was Here is a gorgeous pixel RPG that is inspired by 8 and 16 bit classics. Featuring a groundbreaking combat system and a deep, charming story about the value of life, Nadia was Here lets you play an oldschool RPG in a brand new way!'),
(7901, 'MedusaÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Labyrinth is a very short mythological first-person horror game set in ancient Greece. It takes myths and legends that have stayed with us for over 2000 years and mix them together with modern gameplay. The game lets you explore murky catacombs and follow along a classic, tragic story.'),
(7902, 'Enjoy an original card game set in mystical Ancient Egypt. Work your way up from a small tribe to a flourishing Empire along the Nile. Build huge, unbelievable monuments which tower above vast cities, win the Gods favour and become the mightiest Pharaoh.'),
