(7947, 'Vanquish: The Adventures of Lady Exton is a 2D platformer set in a quirky cyberpunk inspired world. Science has altered things in recent times. It\'s now become a fight for survival. Kidnapped, escaped and armed with only a parasol, Lady Exton must bring back peace to the human strongholds!'),
(7948, 'HoPiKo is an intense speed run platformer where you get to save gaming. Jump from platform to platform avoiding death, exploiting shortcuts and ripping through 100s of hand-crafted levels, each one dropped into a 5-stage mini run designed to break your mind!'),
(7949, 'You are the best pilot of Republic. Your mission is cease the launch of enemy nuclear missile.'),
(7950, 'Find a way to destroy the ancient artifacts!'),
(7951, 'ZeGame is a beautiful puzzle game with complex but rewarding puzzles in three dimensions. Discover the new surroundings in every world, each having their own unique look and feel.'),
(7952, 'A Blind Legend is the first-ever action-adventure game without video where ears replace eyes! Discover the original, innovative sensory experience of binaural 3D sound.'),
(7953, 'GoNNER is a tough as hell procedurally-generated 2D platformer with roguelike elements, following the largely misunderstood and altruistic Ikk on a journey to cheer up his only friend in this world - a giant landbound whale named Sally - by searching for just the right trinket in the deep and dark places nearby.'),
(7954, 'SQUIDS FROM SPACE is a team-based PvP top-down shooter where humans and the sinister Squid aliens wage war for the future of the Earth!'),
(7955, 'State of Mind is a futuristic thriller game delving into transhumanism. The game explores themes of separation, disjuncture and reunification, in a world that is torn between a dystopian material reality and a utopian virtual future.'),
(7956, 'A 8-bit retro action platformer that goes beyond just pixels and chiptunes'),
(7957, 'Enter the Kingdom of the Queen of the Night. Start your journey through the lands of mystery and magic as prince Tamino. Choose your steps wisely, build your path avoiding traps, deadly serpents or earth quakes. But know no fear, lose no hope and remember that you are the master of your own path.'),
(7958, 'A sci-fi, yuri visual novel with a dollop of mystery.'),
(7959, 'Top-down view 2D racing game with realistic handling, online leaderboards, 4-player local split-screen races, a deep career mode where you ascend divisions in the Roadclub League to one day finally challenge the Roadclub Master in an epic Showdown.'),
(7960, 'If you woke up alone in the darkness and trapped... What would you do? Run away or continue? I only say you... When the darkness hunts you, you dont know what is real...'),
(7961, 'Earth Space Colonies is a strategy-simulation game where you build space colonies around the Solar system. Establish a first self-sustaining colony on the Red planet with ultimate goal of terraforming Mars. Play three story campaigns all at once: terraform Mars, fight on Ceres and explore Ganymede.'),
(7962, 'About Project Graviton&quot;Project Graviton&quot; is a platformer game in which users will control the character Bob, whom after stumbling into a secret section of his workplace, gains possession of a Gravity Suit and learns of its capabilities.'),
