(8095, '&quot;So you wish to be able to easily stock up on potion ingredients, eh?&quot; The morning after hearing these words, a dungeon had appeared beneath the potion store! Furious that someone had dug a dungeon in the shop without her permission, Pastel begins her underground investigation...'),
