(8098, 'Engage in furious tank combat using the latest armored vehicles in the next gen multiplayer tank shooter. Choose cooperative missions, PvP battles or our exclusive hybrid battle mode. Attack and dominate war theaters ranging from desolate to urban, and crush your enemies on the modern battlefield!'),
