(9018, 'To escape the city of Starkham and start your new life, you get your friend Preston to set up a meeting with the local loanshark, Sweaty Mike. After foolishly borrowing $2,000 to start your fledgling drug dealing career, you embark on a timed mission to sell as many drugs as possible throughout the city.'),
(9019, 'An exciting adventure in a story of ancient Chinese setting.Visual Novel with multiple endings to explore.'),
(9020, 'Zenodyne R is a new 90s-style shoot-em-up game filled with YM2612 music and real Blast Processing action, where your reflexes and patience will be tested in their entirety! Packed with 6 crazy stages filled wtih bosses, 5 unique ships, unlockables, branching paths and more!'),
(9021, 'An artistic narrative designed to evoke a surreal feeling in the player on a psychological level. Platformer-puzzle-advanture with a handful of different endings!'),
