(9023, 'Hey, boy! I am the Deputy Mayor of Crist City. My secretary has already told you the purchasing price of the wardening position of Pompeii Prison, right? Come on son, make up your mind! There are a lot of people competing for this position. I donÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t have time and patience to waste on you!'),
