(9078, 'Max is in trouble. He pissed off his cat Lula and now she\'s out to get him. And Lula is far from sweet. She is vicious, cold and unforgiving. More dangerous than Lula are her traps deadly and brutal killing contraptions with Max\'s name written all over them.'),
(9079, 'Mini Golf Mundo is a fun casual game suitable to players of all ages and experience levels. Your task is to Putt the ball to victory across 4 challenging courses with a total of 72 holes to complete. You can choose to play alone or invite friends and family to partake in a 4-player turn-based tournament.'),
