(9087, 'Super Comboman is a colorful beat Ã¢â‚¬Ëœem up with wacky characters and fast-paced fighting game combat set in a destructible sticker based world. Fluid combos and upgradable moves allow you to smash and juggle enemies with air and ground combos, while developing your own style in the process.'),
