(9093, 'Hang on to your cockpit seat! Go for a ride through this holographic miniature Solar System, and then squint your eyes in the intense light of a few of the largest known stars. Enjoy curated photos and facts along the way, at your own pace. Great care has been taken to ensure a comfortable VR experience.'),
