(9443, 'The Lords of The Earth Flame is a novel game created in the best traditions of interactive fiction and text-based role-playing. Non-linear structure, rich text core, and the Ã¢â‚¬Å“analogÃ¢â‚¬Â feel of times past are certain to provide unforgettable gaming experience for hours on end.'),
(9444, 'Freebie is a casual game where you launch a ball against a paddle and hit a green surface. Be careful not to hit the red surfaces or youll lose a life!'),
(9445, 'SPAERA is a head-to-head puzzle fighting game, using an unique match-3 cascading mechanic as its core system. The world of SPAERA is heavily inspired by characters, gameplay and themes from games that we loved to play as we were growing up.'),
