(9449, 'In this puzzle, you only have to draw one continuous line. There are 96 puzzles on &quot;Normal&quot;-mode and 96 puzzles in &quot;Time&quot;-mode. Each puzzles can have many different solutions. This is game is Outer Heaven works integrated with achievements, badges, trading cards and more.'),
(9450, 'Space Radiance its arcade game with rpg system. Protect green glow against physical objects using a variety of improvements.'),
(9451, 'KARAKARA. It is the sound of aridity. It is the sound of dry asphalt and sandy winds. It is the sound of relentless sunshine, as well as the sound of a withering race.'),
