(9585, 'Principia: Master of Science is a simulation game with the theme of European science in 17th century. Choose one of 12 real scientists from the era of Isaac Newton and proceed with your research. It is a time when even the term &quot;Science&quot; did not exist. Who can be the master of science?'),
